Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:52.11,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}却以为彼此道路相左
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:55.41,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}让我们高举那被遗忘的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:58.16,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}踏荒野前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:02.54,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}盈盈微笑 滚滚泪珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:08.09,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}皆不可遗留于此地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:12.72,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}夏影倒映 白帜高扬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:20.18,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}那是你我的无名之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:25.69,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}在遥无尽头的道路彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:28.98,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}那一线光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:30.82,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}牵动万千心绪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:34.70,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}深信头顶之青空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:39.91,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}启明星高悬东方
